Mineral Town
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0001]
Your new life in Mineral Town has just begun!
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0002]
There are lots of interesting people living here and many
shops that sell everything you need to begin your farming
adventure!
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0003]
The nearby mountain is covered in nature's bounties,
and it has the most wonderful view from its peak.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0004]
As a new farmer, you can try all sorts of things:
raising crops and livestock, foraging and mining
for items, and more!
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0005]
If you're not sure where to start, try talking to the
townsfolk and seeing what advice they have to give.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0006]
We hope you enjoy your wonderful new life as a farmer
in this beautiful little town.
