Stamina & Fatigue
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0022]
Your character has two main stats: Stamina and Fatigue.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0023]
The red berries in the upper-left corner of the screen
represent your Stamina. It goes down when you do things
like use tools.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0024]
Do work like using tools while your Stamina is 0 and you
will build Fatigue.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0025]
Fatigue also builds when you do things like work outside
late at night or in poor weather.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0026]
The face icon in the upper-left corner of the screen
denotes your level of Fatigue. It changes the more
Fatigue you build.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0027]
Build up too much Fatigue and you will collapse and be
sent to the Clinic. Pay careful attention to prevent that!
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0028]
You can restore Stamina and relieve Fatigue by taking
baths and eating food, but the best cure is a good night's
sleep.
