Marriage 101
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0148]
If you would like to marry your special someone, first you
must propose to them.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0149]
To propose, equip the Blue Feather item and then give it
to them. However, a walk down the aisle is not
guaranteed.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0150]
