Breeding Bin. In five days, a kit will be born.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0200]
Kits born on your farm will grow to like you more quickly
than rabbits that are bought.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0201]
Ring the Bell outside your Coop to send your Angora
