Fishing
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0337]
To fish, equip the Fishing Rod and press the Tool Button
to cast the fishing line straight in front of you.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0338]
Once the line is cast, simply sit back and wait for a fish
to bite.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0339]
When a fish bites, the bobber will move violently.
Press the Tool Button at that moment to reel in your
fish.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0340]
If the fish escapes, simply wait until the next fish comes
along and bites.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0341]
If your timing is off, you may only reel in an empty hook.
But don't give up! Cast your line and try again.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0342]
If there aren't any fish where you're fishing,
no matter how long you wait you won't get a bite.
Try somewhere else.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0343]
Different fish can be caught depending on where you fish
