Spring & Autumn Derbies
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0421]
Pay close attention to your horse's stamina while racing
as fast as you can to finish first.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0422]
Press the Confirm Button repeatedly to speed up your
horse. But be aware: the faster they run, the faster
they'll lose stamina.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0423]
You can gauge your horse's stamina by the color of their
bubble. If it's green, they have plenty of stamina.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0424]
As their stamina goes down, the bubble will turn yellow.
Keep pouring on the speed and eventually it will turn red.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0425]
When the bubble is red, no matter how fast you press the
Confirm Button, your horse won't speed up.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0426]
Your horse will recover stamina whenever you are not
pressing the button.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0427]
Balance your horse's stamina carefully by pressing the
button at just the right time and race to first place.
