[0483]
The Nature Sprites
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0484]
Make friends with the Nature Sprites and they will help
you with your chores and even play with you.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0485]
To make friends with them, give them presents! You can
make friends with each individual Nature Sprite.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0486]
Once you are good friends with the Nature Sprites they
will help you with three different chores.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0487]
1. Watering Crops
They will water the crops you are raising on your farm.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0488]
2. Harvesting
They will harvest any ripe crops on your farm and put
them into the Shipping Bin.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0489]
3. Livestock Care
They will feed and brush your animals as well as ship any
of their byproducts.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0490]
The more the Nature Sprites help you with certain
chores, the better and faster they will get at them.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0491]
You can also choose to play with the Nature Sprites to
give them practice with specific chores.
