[0504]
Tending Livestock
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0505]
There are lots of animals available in Mineral Town.
Raise them with love and you will gain much from them.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0506]
There are five different types of animals you can raise:
cows, sheep, alpacas, chickens, and Angora rabbits.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0507]
Cows, sheep, and alpacas live in Barns.
Chickens and Angora rabbits live in Coops.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0508]
You can purchase new animals from a store, or breed
your current animals and raise the babies.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0509]
It's important to feed your animals every day, brush
them, talk to them, and put them out to pasture on
nice days.
<------------------------------------------------------->
[0510]
The more love you show them, the better byproducts
they will produce, so make sure to take very good care
of them!
